<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>   k...I've been more than amiable to listen to what you have to say in the past. <br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->you have been consistantly rude to me in the past, and this post is no exception. <br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>   <br>
But now I'm pretty much getting sick and tired of the &quot;fixes&quot; you propose...Being nothing more than bullshit ideas that, in actuality, screw our class over more than it already is, as well as screwing over melee classes.<br>
<br>
